         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, ¶ 18/9/83. ¶ To the honorable Graham Berry, M.L.A, ¶ Chief Secretary. ¶ Sir...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.09.18</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Graham Berry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Y83/9026, unit 13A, VPRS 1163/P1 inward correspondence files, VA 672 Premier's Office, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">18/9/83.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">To the honorable Graham Berry, M.L.A,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to transmit herewith a richly illustrated volume on plants collected by Dr Wawra von Fernsee, who accompanied their Royal Highnesses the Princes of Coburg Gotha around the world as medical companion.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wawra von Fersee (1883).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I would suggest, that the volume be transmitted to the trustees of the public Library, with a view of being added to the collections of works of that great institution.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the letter from Staffsurgeon Dr Wawra von Fernsee, accompanying this sending by post and arriving yesterday,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he begs to be provided for the botanic Museum of Vienna with the publications, mentioned on the next page, to complete thereby the series of bot. works issued here at the expense of the Victorian Government.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's letter was referred from the Chief Secretary's Department to the Premier's Office on 27 September 1883. On 1 October 1883, the Premier's Secretary, E. Thomas, minuted, presumably for the benefit of the Premier, J. Service: 'Baron von Mueller forwards a richly illustrated Volume on Plants collected by Dr Wawra who attended the Princes Coburg Gotha in their travels | The volume has been placed in the Public Library. | Dr Wawra asks in return for certain of the Baron's Works for the Botanic Museum Vienna | 1. Supply the works? | 2. Should the works be handed over to the Baron for presentation — or presented by the Premier direct?' The next day, 2 October 1883, Thomas wrote to T. Wilson, Under Secretary in the Chief Secretary's Office: 'The Hon. the Premier approves of the presentation being made, and will cause the Books to be forwarded accordingly. Will the Under Secretary please inform the Governt Botanist to this effect, and at the same time obtain from Baron von Mueller, the correct address of Dr Wawra von Fernsee in order that the parcel may be forwarded?' Wilson on the same day forwarded the file to M, who returned it on 3 October minuted: 'With expression of thanks for approval of this reciprocative sending, I beg to give the address: Chevalier Heinrich Wawra Von Fernsee, M.D. Surgeon-Major of the Imperial Navy of Austria, Vienne'. On 5 October, Thomas asked the Government Printer, J. Ferres, to forward to him the books M had listed, and this Ferres did on 10 October except for Decade I of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'Vegetable Fossils'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which Thomas had to obtain instead from the Mines Department.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>On 24 October, Thomas wrote to Wawra von Fernsee on behalf of the Premier, thanking him for his donation and informing him of the collection of M's works that was being forwarded to him in reciprocation through Victoria's Agent-General in London. The whole of the earlier file was returned to Thomas on 30 October 'For the information of the Secretary to the Premier'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obed. servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Eucalyptographia, Decades VI, VII, VIII.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B80.13.14, B82.13.17.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Fragmenta phytographiae Australiae vol. XI.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B82.05.22.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Vegetable fossils of the auriferous drifts, Decades I and II.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B74.13.07, B83.13.04.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Systematic Census of Australian Plants.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn6" n="7">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B83.03.04.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
